《'''莫比烏斯'''》（{{lang-ko|뫼비우스}}，{{lang-en|''Moebius''}}） 是一部韩国导演[[金基德|金基德]]编剧、执导的家庭倫理恐怖片。内容涉及切斷[[生殖器|生殖器]]和[[近親性交|母子乱伦]]场景，因此受到了韩国映像部门的严格审查，被評定為限制放映（제한상영가）。在剪輯掉表達重要主題「如同心臟一般」的場景之後，才降級为青少年不宜（청소년관람불가）公映。<ref name="SceneAsia">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2013/08/07/korean-censors-lower-rating-on-controversial-movie/ |title=Korean Censors Lower Rating on Controversial Movie |accessdate=2013-08-15 |work=Scene Asia |archive-date=2018-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807094545/https://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2013/08/07/korean-censors-lower-rating-on-controversial-movie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="twitchfilm">{{cite web |url=http://twitchfilm.com/2013/06/not-coming-to-screens-any-time-soon-kim-ki-duks-moebius-effectively-banned-in-korea.html |title=Not Coming To Screens Any Time Soon: Kim Ki-duk's ''Moebius'' Effectively Banned In Korea |accessdate=2013-08-15 |work=Twitch |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813091435/http://twitchfilm.com/2013/06/not-coming-to-screens-any-time-soon-kim-ki-duks-moebius-effectively-banned-in-korea.html |archivedate=2013-08-13 }}</ref><ref name="screendaily">{{cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/moebius-cleared-for-release-with-cuts/5059049.article?blocktitle=News&contentID=2613# |title=Moebius cleared for release with cuts |accessdate=2013-08-15 |work=Screen Daily |archive-date=2018-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807094554/https://www.screendaily.com/news/moebius-cleared-for-release-with-cuts/5059049.article?blocktitle=News&contentID=2613 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="chosun">{{cite web |url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2013/08/21/2013082101151.html |title=Kim Ki-duk's 'Moebius' Due Out in Early September |accessdate=2013-08-15 |work=Chosun |archive-date=2017-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805015105/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2013/08/21/2013082101151.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinese.joins.com/big5/article.do?method=detail&art_id=107713&category=003003|title=金基德新作「莫比烏斯」在結束第三次審議後成功獲準在國內上映|accessdate=2013-08-08|archive-date=2018-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807064317/http://chinese.joins.com/big5/article.do?method=detail&art_id=107713&category=003003|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[第70届威尼斯影展|第70届威尼斯影展]]上全球首映無刪減版本<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/out-of-competition/ |title=Out of Competition |accessdate=2013-07-27 |work=labiennale |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728070801/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/out-of-competition |archivedate=2013-07-28 }}</ref><ref name="Guardian">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up/ |title=Venice film festival 2013: the full line-up |accessdate=2013-07-27 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725191906/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up |dead-url=no }}</ref>，韩国于2013年9月5日上映。

另外本片於香港及台灣推出上映和發行的版本均為未刪剪版。

